---
title: Sichuan Honey-Glazed Beef Rissoles with Roast Veggie & Corn Toss
description: Rissoles are a crowd-pleasing dinner winner, but when you add our All-American spice blend and toss them in sriracha and
honey, they’re even harder to refuse! This plate also includes a serving of colourful roast veggies for a rainbow of delights.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
